## 12. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)

### Can I use this without internet?

Yes! Shamal Tools works completely offline. No internet connection is required for any features.

### What happens if an image has no GPS?

Images without GPS data:
- Won't appear on maps in the Map Organizer Tool
- Will be counted in the "Missing GPS" statistic in the Geotagging Tool
- Can still be renamed with the Flight Renaming Tool
- Can have GPS added using the Geotagging Tool

### Can I rename files multiple times?

Yes, but:
- Each rename creates a new set of filenames
- Use the "Undo Last" feature to reverse the most recent rename
- Original files remain unchanged in their original location

### Does the app modify original images?

No. By default:
- Original images are never modified
- New files are created during export operations
- You control where new files are saved
- Backup information allows undoing operations

